{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1777038214821,"sessionID":"ses_24044dc1dffewAlZ3GwcibflOU","part":{"id":"prt_dbfbb46a3001HVtS5K5G8rwbyp","messageID":"msg_dbfbb287f001kIj8zvO372rofy","sessionID":"ses_24044dc1dffewAlZ3GwcibflOU","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1777038228562,"sessionID":"ses_24044dc1dffewAlZ3GwcibflOU","part":{"id":"prt_dbfbb4d92001yLue9bISArUJwo","messageID":"msg_dbfbb287f001kIj8zvO372rofy","sessionID":"ses_24044dc1dffewAlZ3GwcibflOU","type":"text","text":"Here's a plan for creating the Snake game:\n\n1.  **HTML Structure:** I'll start by creating the basic HTML structure, including a `<canvas>` for the game board, a score display, and a \"Game Over\" message area with a restart button.\n2.  **CSS Styling:** Next, I'll add inline CSS to give the game a polished and modern look, ensuring it's centered and visually appealing.\n3.  **JavaScript Logic:** Finally, I'll implement the game's logic in JavaScript, covering the snake's movement, food generation, collision detection (with walls and itself), scoring, and the complete game loop, all controlled by arrow keys.\n\nI will now create the `index.html` file with the full game code.","time":{"start":1777038216594,"end":1777038228561},"metadata":{"copilot":{"reasoningOpaque":""}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777038228569,"sessionID":"ses_24044dc1dffewAlZ3GwcibflOU","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_MHx4SjhtQVJRQ3daVENncWhTajY","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Snake Game</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            color: #f0f0f0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            height: 100vh;\n            margin: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        #game-container {\n            position: relative;\n            width: 400px;\n            height: 400px;\n            border: 4px solid #4cc9f0;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            background-color: #0d1b2a;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        canvas {\n            display: block;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        #score-container {\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n        }\n        \n        #score-container span {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #4cc9f0;\n        }\n\n        #game-over-overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.85);\n            display: none;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        #game-over-overlay h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: #f72585;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(247, 37, 133, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        #restart-button {\n            background-color: #4cc9f0;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 24px;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.1s;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        #restart-button:hover {\n            background-color: #3a86ff;\n        }\n        \n        #restart-button:active {\n            transform: scale(0.95);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>Snake</h1>\n    <div id=\"game-container\">\n        <canvas id=\"game-canvas\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\"></canvas>\n        <div id=\"game-over-overlay\">\n            <h2>Game Over</h2>\n            <button id=\"restart-button\">Restart</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"score-container\">Score: <span id=\"score\">0</span></div>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const canvas = document.getElementById('game-canvas');\n            const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n            const scoreEl = document.getElementById('score');\n            const gameOverOverlay = document.getElementById('game-over-overlay');\n            const restartButton = document.getElementById('restart-button');\n\n            const gridSize = 20;\n            const tileCount = canvas.width / gridSize;\n\n            let snake, food, direction, score, gameLoop, isGameOver;\n\n            function init() {\n                snake = [{ x: 10, y: 10 }];\n                food = {};\n                direction = { x: 0, y: 0 };\n                score = 0;\n                isGameOver = false;\n                \n                scoreEl.textContent = score;\n                gameOverOverlay.style.display = 'none';\n                \n                placeFood();\n                if (gameLoop) clearInterval(gameLoop);\n                gameLoop = setInterval(update, 100);\n            }\n\n            function placeFood() {\n                food = {\n                    x: Math.floor(Math.random() * tileCount),\n                    y: Math.floor(Math.random() * tileCount)\n                };\n\n                // Ensure food doesn't spawn on the snake\n                for (let part of snake) {\n                    if (part.x === food.x && part.y === food.y) {\n                        placeFood();\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n\n            function update() {\n                if (isGameOver) return;\n\n                const head = { x: snake[0].x + direction.x, y: snake[0].y + direction.y };\n                \n                // Wall collision\n                if (head.x < 0 || head.x >= tileCount || head.y < 0 || head.y >= tileCount) {\n                    return gameOver();\n                }\n\n                // Self collision\n                for (let i = 1; i < snake.length; i++) {\n                    if (head.x === snake[i].x && head.y === snake[i].y) {\n                        return gameOver();\n                    }\n                }\n                \n                snake.unshift(head);\n\n                // Food collision\n                if (head.x === food.x && head.y === food.y) {\n                    score++;\n                    scoreEl.textContent = score;\n                    placeFood();\n                } else {\n                    snake.pop();\n                }\n\n                draw();\n            }\n\n            function draw() {\n                // Background\n                ctx.fillStyle = '#0d1b2a';\n                ctx.fillRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);\n\n                // Snake\n                for (let i = 0; i < snake.length; i++) {\n                    ctx.fillStyle = i === 0 ? '#4cc9f0' : '#3a86ff'; // Head is a different color\n                    ctx.fillRect(snake[i].x * gridSize, snake[i].y * gridSize, gridSize - 2, gridSize - 2);\n                }\n\n                // Food\n                ctx.fillStyle = '#f72585';\n                ctx.fillRect(food.x * gridSize, food.y * gridSize, gridSize - 2, gridSize - 2);\n            }\n\n            function gameOver() {\n                isGameOver = true;\n                clearInterval(gameLoop);\n                gameOverOverlay.style.display = 'flex';\n            }\n\n            function handleKeyPress(e) {\n                const key = e.key;\n                const goingUp = direction.y === -1;\n                const goingDown = direction.y === 1;\n                const goingLeft = direction.x === -1;\n                const goingRight = direction.x === 1;\n\n                if ((key === 'ArrowUp' || key === 'w') && !goingDown) {\n                    direction = { x: 0, y: -1 };\n                } else if ((key === 'ArrowDown' || key === 's') && !goingUp) {\n                    direction = { x: 0, y: 1 };\n                } else if ((key === 'ArrowLeft' || key === 'a') && !goingRight) {\n                    direction = { x: -1, y: 0 };\n                } else if ((key === 'ArrowRight' || key === 'd') && !goingLeft) {\n                    direction = { x: 1, y: 0 };\n                }\n            }\n            \n            document.addEventListener('keydown', handleKeyPress);\n            restartButton.addEventListener('click', init);\n\n            init();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n","filePath":"/Users/t969275/Code/Scienta/multisnake/gemini-2.5-pro/index.html"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/t969275/Code/Scienta/multisnake/gemini-2.5-pro/index.html","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"Users/t969275/Code/Scienta/multisnake/gemini-2.5-pro/index.html","time":{"start":1777038228556,"end":1777038228565}},"metadata":{"copilot":{"reasoningOpaque":""}},"id":"prt_dbfbb7c44001CaHd6YY5U4XnGz","sessionID":"ses_24044dc1dffewAlZ3GwcibflOU","messageID":"msg_dbfbb287f001kIj8zvO372rofy"}}
